Global Mobile Waterproof Bag Market Insights
Mobile Waterproof Bag Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Mobile Waterproof Bag Market Overview
The global mobile waterproof bag market was valued at approximately USD 0.3 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 0.5 billion by 2032, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of about 7% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing need to protect mobile devices from water damage, especially as smartphones become more integral to daily life and outdoor activities. The market encompasses various types of waterproof bags, including those made from materials like PVC, TPU, and others, catering to diverse applications such as bathing, diving, and other water-related activities. Manufacturers are focusing on developing advanced, durable, and user-friendly waterproof solutions to meet the rising demand.

